# CALEX Digital Business Card

Static GitHub Pages-ready e-business card for Mohammed Siddique.

## Files

- `index.html` - the card markup and contact links
- `styles.css` - the full visual design
- `assets/profile.png` - portrait image
- `assets/contact-qr.svg` - QR code containing the vCard contact
- `mohammed-siddique.vcf` - downloadable contact card

## Host on GitHub Pages

1. Create a new GitHub repository.
2. Upload the contents of this folder to the repository root.
3. Go to **Settings > Pages**.
4. Set **Source** to **Deploy from a branch**.
5. Select `main` and `/root`, then save.

GitHub will publish the card at:

`https://YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME.github.io/YOUR-REPOSITORY-NAME/`

## Edit Details

Update the visible phone, email, website, LinkedIn URL, and service text in `index.html`.

Update the QR/contact download details in `mohammed-siddique.vcf`, then regenerate the QR:

```bash
python3 -m pip install reportlab
python3 tools/generate_qr.py
```

:root {
  --bg: #040607;
  --panel: #0a0d0f;
  --panel-soft: #11161a;
  --gold: #f4bd37;
  --gold-dark: #b87814;
  --gold-light: #ffe88b;
  --red: #e4101a;
  --text: #f7f7f2;
  --muted: #c9ccd0;
  --line: rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.6);
  --shadow: 0 26px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
  background: #020303;
}

body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  margin: 0;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  padding: 28px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 18% 14%, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.17), transparent 28%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 82% 85%, rgba(228, 16, 26, 0.13), transparent 25%),
    linear-gradient(135deg, #020303 0%, #0b0f11 55%, #020303 100%);
}

a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
}

svg {
  display: block;
  fill: none;
  stroke: currentColor;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
  stroke-width: 1.8;
}

.card-shell {
  position: relative;
  width: min(100%, 1050px);
  min-height: 1560px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
  gap: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 46px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  background:
    linear-gradient(110deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055), transparent 24%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 42% 35%, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.08), transparent 32%),
    linear-gradient(150deg, #060809 0%, #0a0f12 48%, #030405 100%);
}

.card-shell::before,
.card-shell::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.card-shell::before {
  inset: auto -10% -58px -10%;
  height: 128px;
  background:
    linear-gradient(160deg, transparent 0 13%, var(--red) 13% 25%, transparent 25% 75%, var(--red) 75% 87%, transparent 87%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.28) 70%, var(--gold) 100%);
  border-radius: 55% 55% 0 0;
}

.card-shell::after {
  top: 235px;
  right: -26px;
  width: 260px;
  height: 105px;
  transform: rotate(-45deg);
  background:
    linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0 16%, var(--gold) 16% 27%, #111 27% 49%, transparent 49% 55%, var(--red) 55% 66%, transparent 66%);
  opacity: 0.94;
}

.brand-panel,
.solutions-panel {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  padding: 42px 48px;
}

.brand-panel {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: stretch;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.42);
}

.portrait-wrap {
  position: relative;
  width: min(76%, 420px);
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  margin: 0 auto 26px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  padding: 7px;
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold) 42%, var(--gold-dark) 58%, var(--gold-light));
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 2px rgba(255, 241, 150, 0.35),
    0 0 35px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.72),
    inset 0 0 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

.portrait-wrap::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 15px;
  border-radius: inherit;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
}

.portrait {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: block;
  border-radius: inherit;
  object-fit: cover;
  background: #161616;
}

.identity {
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.eyebrow {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 0.86rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  font-weight: 800;
}

h1 {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: clamp(3.1rem, 6.1vw, 4.5rem);
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  font-weight: 900;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 0 #6e430d, 0 0 18px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.32);
}

.gold-rule {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin: 26px 0 18px;
  color: var(--gold);
}

.gold-rule::before,
.gold-rule::after,
.section-title span {
  content: "";
  height: 2px;
  flex: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
}

.gold-rule span {
  width: 11px;
  height: 11px;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  background: var(--gold);
  box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.7);
}

.role {
  margin: 0 0 22px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  text-transform: none;
}

.contact-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 15px;
  margin: 0;
  font-style: normal;
}

.contact-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 15px;
  min-width: 0;
}

.contact-row strong {
  display: block;
  overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  font-size: 1.83rem;
  line-height: 1.12;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.contact-row small {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 4px;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 1.18rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.icon {
  width: 58px;
  height: 58px;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  color: var(--gold);
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 18px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.12);
}

.icon svg {
  width: 31px;
  height: 31px;
}

.quick-contact {
  margin-top: 28px;
}

.section-title {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-align: center;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.quick-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 16px 14px;
  margin-top: 22px;
}

.quick-button {
  min-height: 78px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  padding: 12px 15px;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 10px;
  color: var(--text);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015));
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 18px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.09);
  font-size: 1.03rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.12;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: transform 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
}

.quick-button:hover,
.quick-button:focus-visible {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  border-color: var(--gold-light);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.18), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025));
}

.quick-button svg {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  width: 43px;
  height: 43px;
  color: var(--gold);
  fill: rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.22);
}

.solutions-panel {
  min-width: 0;
  padding-top: 86px;
}

.map-dots {
  position: absolute;
  top: 18px;
  right: 22px;
  width: 295px;
  height: 180px;
  opacity: 0.43;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, var(--gold-dark) 1.6px, transparent 1.7px);
  background-size: 7px 7px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 0 62%, transparent 72%);
}

.brand-mark {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  margin-left: 8px;
}

.brand-mark h2 {
  margin: 0;
  color: #f8f8f5;
  font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 7vw, 5.2rem);
  line-height: 0.8;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  font-weight: 950;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
}

.logo-a {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  color: transparent;
  width: 0.72em;
}

.logo-a::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0.05em 0.06em 0 0.02em;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red) 0 48%, transparent 49% 56%, #fff 57%);
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 100%, 69% 100%, 52% 56%, 33% 100%, 0 100%);
}

.brand-mark p {
  margin: 6px 0 0 92px;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.36em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.tagline {
  margin: 62px 0 0 12px;
  color: #f3f3ef;
  font-size: 1.68rem;
  line-height: 1.28;
  font-weight: 760;
}

.tagline strong {
  color: var(--gold);
}

.star-line {
  position: relative;
  height: 35px;
  margin: 18px 32px 26px 6px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.6);
}

.star-line span {
  position: absolute;
  top: -8px;
  left: 45%;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  background: radial-gradient(circle, #fff 0 18%, var(--gold) 20% 50%, transparent 52%);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 9px var(--gold));
}

.solutions-card {
  position: relative;
  margin: 18px 20px 22px 32px;
  padding: 82px 40px 30px 54px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 14px;
  background: linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 28px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.08);
}

.solutions-card h3 {
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  left: 28px;
  right: 28px;
  min-height: 78px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 18px;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 12px 22px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 232, 139, 0.7);
  border-radius: 14px;
  color: #0a0b0b;
  background:
    linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45), transparent 30%),
    linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold) 46%, #c48519 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
  font-size: 1.45rem;
  font-weight: 950;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.solutions-card h3 svg {
  width: 42px;
  height: 42px;
  stroke-width: 1.9;
}

.solutions-card ul {
  display: grid;
  gap: 27px;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none;
}

.solutions-card li {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 64px;
  color: #f2f2ee;
  font-size: 1.45rem;
  line-height: 1.18;
}

.solutions-card li::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: -5px;
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  border: 3px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 16px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.18);
}

.solutions-card li::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 11px;
  top: 6px;
  width: 16px;
  height: 9px;
  transform: rotate(-45deg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
  border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
}

.qr-card {
  display: grid;
  justify-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 18px;
}

.qr-frame {
  position: relative;
  width: min(76%, 330px);
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  padding: 15px;
  border: 5px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35), 0 0 20px rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.18);
}

.qr-frame img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: block;
}

.qr-logo {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  width: 70px;
  height: 70px;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  border: 6px solid #fff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  color: var(--red);
  background: #080909;
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  font-weight: 1000;
  line-height: 1;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}

.tap-button {
  width: min(82%, 360px);
  min-height: 76px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 11px 18px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 232, 139, 0.8);
  border-radius: 14px;
  color: #080909;
  text-align: left;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  background:
    linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5), transparent 33%),
    linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold) 45%, #c7861c);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
}

.tap-button svg {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  stroke-width: 2;
}

.tap-button strong {
  display: block;
  font-size: 1.55rem;
  line-height: 1;
  font-weight: 950;
}

.tap-button small {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 900;
}

.service-strip {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  min-height: 210px;
  padding: 0 44px 38px;
}

.service-card {
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  align-content: end;
  justify-items: center;
  min-height: 210px;
  padding: 24px 18px 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-left: 1px solid rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.55);
  text-align: center;
}

.service-card:first-child {
  border-left: 0;
}

.service-card::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0 0 48px;
  opacity: 0.8;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 35%, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.28), transparent 32%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 28, 36, 0.58), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)),
    var(--tile-bg);
  mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, black, transparent 95%);
}

.industrial { --tile-bg: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.16) 0 3px, transparent 3px 23px); }
.marine { --tile-bg: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(35, 80, 98, 0.52), rgba(2, 8, 10, 0.2)); }
.global { --tile-bg: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(53, 150, 188, 0.58), transparent 45%); }
.vision { --tile-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 114, 62, 0.62), rgba(8, 35, 50, 0.28)); }

.service-card svg,
.service-card h3 {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.service-card svg {
  width: 54px;
  height: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  color: #f7f7f4;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
}

.service-card h3 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.02rem;
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

@media (max-width: 940px) {
  body {
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .card-shell {
    min-height: auto;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    border-radius: 28px;
  }

  .card-shell::after {
    display: none;
  }

  .brand-panel {
    border-right: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.42);
  }

  .brand-panel,
  .solutions-panel {
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }

  .solutions-panel {
    padding-top: 38px;
  }

  .portrait-wrap {
    width: min(74%, 330px);
  }

  .role {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .contact-row strong {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .quick-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .brand-mark h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.9rem, 17vw, 4.9rem);
  }

  .brand-mark p {
    margin-left: 56px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.27em;
  }

  .tagline {
    margin-top: 34px;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .solutions-card {
    margin: 34px 0 22px;
    padding: 72px 24px 28px;
  }

  .solutions-card h3 {
    left: 18px;
    right: 18px;
    font-size: 1.12rem;
  }

  .solutions-card li {
    padding-left: 54px;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
  }

  .service-strip {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    padding: 0 20px 34px;
  }

  .service-card:nth-child(3) {
    border-left: 0;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 520px) {
  body {
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .card-shell {
    border-radius: 22px;
  }

  .brand-panel,
  .solutions-panel {
    padding: 26px 18px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-row {
    grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr;
  }

  .icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .icon svg {
    width: 25px;
    height: 25px;
  }

  .quick-button {
    min-height: 66px;
  }

  .qr-frame {
    width: min(92%, 310px);
  }

  .service-strip {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding-inline: 18px;
  }

  .service-card {
    border-left: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(244, 189, 55, 0.35);
  }
}
